OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F366A1777475480
OL,3,CTwin sisters among five in court
OL,4,Caccused of veteran's murder
OL,6,FTwin sisters Britney and Bethany
OL,7,FNaylor - both 20 and from Hull - and
OL,8,F21-year-old Blackpool woman Shaytoyia,
OL,9,Fwho was previously named by police as
OL,10,FShaytiya Farrow, appeared alongside
OL,11,FKristjan Suits, 34, and 27-year-old
OL,12,FLucasz Matusiak, both from Hull.
OL,14,FProsecutor Adrian Strong told the
OL,15,Fcourt a trial would likely be arranged
OL,16,Ffor either September or November this
OL,17,Fyear.
OL,1,Woz5~k4{$z%~s1z5jw=hw1         G3/5
