OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F366A1777475480
OL,3,CTwin sisters among five in court
OL,4,Caccused of veteran's murder
OL,6,FAll five defendants spoke only to
OL,7,Fconfirm their names and dates of birth
OL,8,Fand were remanded into custody.
OL,9,FAnother hearing will be held on 7
OL,10,FAugust.
OL,12,FA request from the defence was also
OL,13,Fpassed to Humberside Police for
OL,14,FFacebook posts surrounding the case to
OL,15,Fbe monitored to protect the rights to
OL,16,Fa fair trial.
OL,1,Woz5~k4{$z%~s1z5jw=hw1         G4/5
